{"TopicId":167500,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Kerbin Konstructs Airbase Building for Campaign","CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-13T13:54:35Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-13T13:54:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMe, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166583-dundun92/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022166583\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/166583-dundun92/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@dundun92\u003C/a\u003E, \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179353-dundun93/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022179353\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/179353-dundun93/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@dundun93\u003C/a\u003E, and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/70652-jollygreengi/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002270652\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/70652-jollygreengi/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@JollyGreenGI\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0are about to start working on a sort of BDA campaign, consisting of multiple missions in KSP scenarios format. To do this, I would like to spread a selection of stock, simple airbases around Kerbin, fit for the occasion. My estimate is that we will need anywhere from \u003Cs\u003E25 to 50 airbases\u003C/s\u003E\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003E10 to 15 of them actually\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0(but fear not\u00A0because many of them can be the same stock model, just altered by a tiny margin). Since I am hard-pressed for time in real life and have no present copy of KSP, I have no choice but to search for volunteers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would like to suggest some requirements for each base:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- The bases should look similar. These aren\u0027t diverse airports, these are military airfields. Think of the bases in DCS, but much smaller and more simple.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- The bases should have\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Ea)\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A04 plane hangars,\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Eb)\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A01 or 2 runway(s),\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Ec)\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0A tower,\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Ed)\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A02 to 4 fuel tanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- Try to make each base component in close proximity to each other: no huge, complex taxiways.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- You are free to add your own small changes into each base to make them different, i.e. orientation changes for runways or hangar blocks, perhaps a small cluster of apartment buildings adjacent to it, etc.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you for your consideration, future volunteer (whoever you are). I hope this project goes well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPS: By the way, \u003Cstrong\u003Eple(ple[please]ase)ase\u003C/strong\u003E state your experience with KerbinSide/Kerbal Konstructs construction, and the dedication you are willing to have. I will PM you if you wish to add to this project, and explain further.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-11-14T03:41:35Z\u0022 title=\u002211/14/2017 03:41  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003ENovember 14, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Matuchkin\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-14T03:40:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: after looking at a map of Kerbin, I realised that I grossly overstated the amount of bases required for this. We would need somewhere around 10-15 of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-14T18:54:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBy the way, i cant use Kerbin-Side, and i would need permission, which i cant get. I can only get Kerbal Konstructs .dll, which means we need to make our own bases using stock assets.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthese are \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/105348-alphaash/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022105348\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/105348-alphaash/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@AlphaAsh\u003C/a\u003Es tutorials on KK base making\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#353c41;font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/94863-11-kerbal-konstructs-v0960-kerbin-isnt-hard/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=1621379\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003EA Guide To Editing And Making Bases With KK\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/94863-11-kerbal-konstructs-v0960-kerbin-isnt-hard/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=2134264\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003EHow to Export Custom Base Packs\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/94863-11/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=2048272\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003ESetting Up a Static Launchsite\u0027s Spawn Point In Unity\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/94863-11/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=2048314\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003ECreating a Configuration File For a Static\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/94863-11/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=1656262\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003EI Make Statics. How Do I Make My Fuel Tanks, erm, Tank?\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/94863-11/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=2007488\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003EHow to Configure a Launchsite Model\u0027s Width and Length\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/94863-11/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=2039721\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;color:#3d6594;\u0022\u003EHow To Configure A Launchsite With LaunchRefund and Recovery Ratings\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/94863-11/\u0026amp;do=findComment\u0026amp;comment=2060446\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022 style=\