Just now, dundun92 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhich means we need to make our own bases using stock assets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGreat idea!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-11-14T22:52:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGuys, try to make them as drab and military as possible: not to stray too far from your comfort zone with these ones (after all they are military). Thanks for your help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBy the way, sometime in the next two months I may get a better computer, so I will be able to actually put in some elbow grease rather than grey matter.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}